<br>
I left the group to invis some monk who had gone LD last time there. I know the cleric of my group (also the leader) was afk so I figured there wouldn't be a pull inc.<br>
<br>
Well, after the invis I disbanded and waited for the re-invite. For some reason our puller missed the afk message from the cleric so he was kind enough to bring in a spider.<br>
The 57 shammy couldn't heal the puller/tank (pally) enough and the chanter couldn't mez it so they decided to simply kill it fast.<br>
<br>
I was the whole time out of the group so missed this and assumed the cleric was back but couldn't invite me because he had to heal.<br>
<br>
I was just doing my normal routine. Pet in the back, lob a couple of SoFB's (enough to not go FM <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   ) and a FoT at the end to circumvent enrage.<br>
<br>
Sure enough, I got the exp. <br>
When I got re-invited I heard about the afk cleric and that they threw everything they had to kill the mob.. that is a windbladed pally, Wake the Dead spider, EoT, 54 water mage pet, charmed goblin, and a chanter, 54 mage, shammy and necro using over half their mana in as much damage as they could.. and I still KSed them without trying.<br>
